{"product_id":"linden-flower-shampoo-with-nordic-birch-extract-250ml","title":"Magrada Hair Stimulating Shampoo With Linden Flower Extract 250ml","description":"\u003cdiv class=\"entry-content\"\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/1-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"anne stiil ilulemmik 2019\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https:\/\/www.magrada.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/2-2-300x300.png\" alt=\"iluteemant proff soovitab\" width=\"100\" height=\"100\"\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eTake the summer with you – the linden flower shampoo with birch extract is a powerful Nordic elixir which supports and accelerates natural hair growth. The sweet scent of the shampoo will take you back to warm summer memories in a blink, bringing a smile to your face even on a bitterly cold winter morning.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe invigorating shampoo will make your hair less frizzy, nurturing and moisturising the structure of the hair and giving it a beautiful gloss and shine. The organic plant extracts support hair growth and improve the elasticity of the hair. The hair is soft, light, flowing after washing!\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe shampoo is suitable for daily use for the entire family, including for sensitive and delicate scalps.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eOrganic Nordic birch extract\u003c\/span\u003e stimulates circulation in the scalp and strengthens the roots, accelerating natural hair growth.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eThe organic aloe extract \u003c\/span\u003ehas a deeply calming and moisturising effect on the skin. Aloe is well-known for its rich vitamin A, C, and E, folic acid, and collagen content.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003ePro-Vitamin B5\u003c\/span\u003e adds healthy elasticity and shine to the hair and improves the structure of processed hair.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\n\u003cspan style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"\u003eNordic linden flower extract\u003c\/span\u003e has a moisturising and softening effect suitable for a sensitive or irritated scalp.\u003c\/li\u003e\n\u003c\/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eHow to use:\u003c\/strong\u003e Apply the shampoo thoroughly on wet hair. Massage into a lather. Rinse. Repeat the procedure, if necessary.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eStore at a temperature of 5 to 25 degrees. When storing, protect from direct sunlight. Do not store the product near heaters or other heat sources.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eIngredients:\u003c\/strong\u003e Aqua, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Sodium Cocoamphoacetate, Disodium Lauryl Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Chloride, Citric Acid, Argan Oil Glycereth-8 Esters*, Parfum, Aloe Barbadensis (Aloe Vera) Leaf Extract, Palmitamidopropyltrimonium Chloride, Propylene Glycol, Isostearamide MIPA, Betula Alba (Birch) Leaf Extract, Glycerin, Alcohol, Panthenol, Tilia Cordata (Linden) Flower Extract, Glyceryl Laurate, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Potassium Sorbate, Sodium Benzoate, Hexyl Cinnamal, Geraniol\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e*COSMOS Certified Organic Ingredient\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eIngredients of natural origin: \u003cspan\u003e97,44%.\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe list of ingredients may be changed. Please see the packaging for the updated and most accurate list of ingredients.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003eparaben-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e sulphate-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e silicone-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e vegan \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e cruelty-free \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e hand-made \u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e|\u003c\/span\u003e\u003cspan\u003e with a minimal list of ingredients\u003c\/span\u003e\u003c\/p\u003e\n\u003c\/div\u003e","brand":"Magrada Organic Cosmetics","offers":[{"title":"Default Title","offer_id":48927725683015,"sku":"","price":12.9,"currency_code":"EUR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0790\/6829\/9591\/files\/magrada-hair-stimulating-shampoo-with-linden-flower-extract-250ml-8194248.png?v=1763665704","url":"https:\/\/bioskina.com\/products\/linden-flower-shampoo-with-nordic-birch-extract-250ml","provider":"bioskina","version":"1.0","type":"link"}